com.rey.material.app

Class ToolbarManager

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.rey.material.app.ToolbarManager

  • public class ToolbarManager
extends java.lang.Object
    A Manager class to help handling Toolbar used as ActionBar in ActionBarActivity. It help grouping ActionItem in Toolbar and only show the items of current group. It also help manager state of navigation icon. Created by Rey on 1/6/2015.
